  <brief_title>Plasma Glucagon-like Peptide-1 Levels and Acute Myocardial Infarction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prognostic Value of Plasma Glucagon-like Peptide-1 Levels in Acute Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
